 'Jost', sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(44,33,24,0.16);\">\n\n  <!-- HEADER -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; padding-bottom: 18px; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #2C2118;\">\n    <div style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #2C2118; line-height: 1;\">Prism + Fleur<\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #9C8E79; line-height: 1;\">AFFILIATE CIRCLE<\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- DISCOUNT CODE -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; gap: 14px; padding: 46px 0 44px; border-bottom: 1px solid #DBD1C1;\">\n    <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #9C8E79; text-transform: uppercase;\">Your Personal Discount Code<\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 48px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #2C2118; line-height: 1;\">AFFILIATECIRCLE30<\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #7C6E5C; line-height: 1.6; white-space: nowrap;\">This is your personal code to use on our website — shop anything from the Prism + Fleur collection.<\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR -->\n  <div style=\"padding: 44px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #DBD1C1;\">\n    <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: #9C8E79; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;\">What We're Looking For<\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #5A4C3D;\">\n      <div>We'd love for our tarot and oracle decks to be featured naturally within your content — woven into your posts, Reels, or Stories in a way that feels genuine to you and your community.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div>In terms of deliverables, we're looking for:<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #B7A88F; flex: none;\">—<\u002Fspan><span>1 Story set (3–5 frames) showing the product in use, with your affiliate code and @prism.and.fleur tagged<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #B7A88F; flex: none;\">—<\u002Fspan><span>3 Reels (15–30 seconds) featuring the product, with your affiliate code in the caption and @prism.and.fleur tagged<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #B7A88F; flex: none;\">—<\u002Fspan><span>2 Feed posts featuring the product, with your affiliate code in the caption and @prism.and.fleur tagged<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #B7A88F; flex: none;\">—<\u002Fspan><span>All content delivered within 3 weeks of receiving your items<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- HOW WE WANT IT TO FEEL -->\n  <div style=\"padding: 44px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #DBD1C1;\">\n    <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: #9C8E79; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;\">How We Want It To Feel<\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #5A4C3D;\">\n      <div style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35; color: #2C2118\">We're not asking you to “sell” this deck, or persuade people that it's for them.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div>We're asking you to share what it actually feels like to own it and use it.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35; color: #2C2118; margin-top: 6px;\">Think of it like this:<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div>You're not talking to the internet. You're talking to one person who might need this in their life — your friend, someone who's listening to you.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div>We're looking for content that feels:<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span>Real, not rehearsed<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv><div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline;\"><span>Calm, honest and grounded<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        \n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35; color: #2C2118; margin-top: 6px\">If it feels calm to make, it will feel calm to watch.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div>Bring your own voice and style to it — that's exactly what we want to see.<\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- REFERENCE EXAMPLES -->\n  <div style=\"padding: 44px 0 4px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: #9C8E79; text-transform: uppercase;\">Reference Examples<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"font-weight: 500; font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: #B7A88F; text-transform: uppercase;\">Video Content<\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #5A4C3D; margin-bottom: 34px; max-width: 620px;\">Click the links below for inspiration — feel free to use these as a reference or simply to get a feel for the kind of content we love:<\u002Fdiv>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px;\">\n      <sc-for list=\"{{ reels }}\" as=\"reel\" hint-placeholder-count=\"5\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px; width: 120px;\">\n          <div style=\"position: relative; width: 120px; padding: 5px; background: #2C2118; border-radius: 26px; box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(44,33,24,0.18);\">\n          <img src=\"{{ reel.thumb }}\" alt=\"{{ reel.type }} reference\" style=\"display: block; width: 110px; height: 236px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 21px;\">\n            <a href=\"{{ reel.url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"View on Instagram\" style=\"position: absolute; inset: 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 4; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 21px;\">\n              <span style=\"width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(245,240,231,0.92); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(44,33,24,0.3); transition: transform 0.15s ease;\">\n                <span style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 14px solid #2C2118; border-top: 9px solid transparent; border-bottom: 9px solid transparent; margin-left: 3px;\"><\u002Fspan>\n              <\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fa><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px;\">\n            <div style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #9C8E79; text-transform: uppercase;\">{{ reel.type }}<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-for>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 44px; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #2C2118;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n\n<\u002Fdiv>\n\n<\u002Fx-dc>\n<script type=\"text/x-dc\" data-dc-script=\"\">\nclass Component extends DCLogic {\n  renderVals() {\n    return {\n      reels: [\n        { id: 'reel-1', type: 'Reel', url: 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/DXjjLfwjHg3/', shortcode: 'DXjjLfwjHg3', thumb: 'data:image/png;base64,' },\n        { id: 'reel-2', type: 'Reel', url: 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/DWUDMYmDVlZ/', shortcode: 'DWUDMYmDVlZ', thumb: 'data:image/